OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FThe chancellor will deliver the Budget
OL,7,Flater today, billed as the most
OL,8,Fconsequential since 2010
OL,10,FRachel Reeves is set to unveil
OL,11,FLabour's first Budget in a generation
OL,12,Ffollowing weeks of speculation and
OL,13,Freports around tax hikes and spending
OL,14,Fcuts.
OL,16,FIt has been billed as the most
OL,17,Fconsequential Budget since 2010, and
OL,18,FLabour warns it has had to make
OL,19,F"difficult decisions" to plug a #22
OL,20,Fbillion black hole it claims the
OL,21,FTories left in their wake.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
