OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FSome measures have already been
OL,7,Fconfirmed, such as a #1 increase to
OL,8,Fthe #2 bus fare cap, scrapping the VAT
OL,9,Fexemption for private schools, axing
OL,10,Fthe winter fuel allowance, and raising
OL,11,Fthe minimum wage by 6.7% to #12.21 per
OL,12,Fhour.
OL,14,FHere are some of the key measures to
OL,15,Fexpect in Reeves' first budget - and
OL,16,Fthe first ever written by a female
OL,17,Fchancellor.
OL,19,FTax hikes and changes
