OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,F- Employer national insurance
OL,7,Fcontributions
OL,9,FReeves is widely expected to increase
OL,10,Femployer national insurance (NI)
OL,11,Fcontributions after she and the prime
OL,12,Fminister both signalled it could be on
OL,13,Fthe cards.
OL,15,FITV News understands the move is
OL,16,Fexpected to be Labour's biggest
OL,17,Frevenue raiser, collecting just shy of
OL,18,F#20 billion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
