OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,F- Income tax
OL,8,FReeves is also expected to extend the
OL,9,Ffreeze on income tax thresholds, which
OL,10,Fsees people pulled into paying higher
OL,11,Frates through a process known as
OL,12,F"fiscal drag".
OL,14,FThe previous Conservative government
OL,15,Ffroze thresholds until 2028 but it is
OL,16,Fthought the chancellor will extend it
OL,17,Fyet further.
OL,19,F- Fuel duty
