OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FAccording to reports, she could be
OL,7,Fconsidering changing some rules around
OL,8,Finheritance tax, including extending
OL,9,Fthe number of years someone has to
OL,10,Fstay alive after passing on wealth as
OL,11,Fa gift from seven to 10 years.
OL,13,FCurrently, the number of people who
OL,14,Fpay inheritance tax is very small -
OL,15,Flast year only 5% of estates were
OL,16,Fcharged an inheritance tax bill. There
OL,17,Fare also quite a lot of exemptions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
