OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FThe funding includes #1.5 billion for
OL,7,Fnew surgical hubs and scanners and #70
OL,8,Fmillion for radiotherapy machines.
OL,10,FAn additional #1.8 billion has been
OL,11,Fallocated for elective appointments
OL,12,Fsince July.
OL,14,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting has
OL,15,Fwarned a "single Budget" cannot fix
OL,16,F"14 years of damage done to the NHS"
OL,17,Fand that the extra money might not
OL,18,Fprevent avoidable deaths, as well as
OL,19,Fanother winter crisis over the coming
OL,20,Fmonths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/16
