OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FHe said: "We will start planning for
OL,7,Fnext winter, this winter, to make sure
OL,8,Fwe see continued, steady improvement
OL,9,Fin our NHS.
OL,11,F"And what this Budget will enable us
OL,12,Fto do is arrest the decline in the NHS
OL,13,Fand start fixing the foundation so we
OL,14,Fcan not only get the NHS back on its
OL,15,Ffeet, but make sure it's fit for the
OL,16,Ffuture as part of our long-term plan."
