OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FThe government has already confirmed a
OL,7,Fraft of measures to boost affordable
OL,8,Fhousing.
OL,10,FIt has pledged #500 million to help
OL,11,Fbuild 5,000 social housing properties,
OL,12,Fbringing the total investment in
OL,13,Fhousing supply to #5 billion.
OL,15,FA further #128 million has already
OL,16,Fbeen confirmed for three projects to
OL,17,Fbuild homes.
