OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FSome #1.4 billion has been announced
OL,7,Falready to rebuild crumbling schools.
OL,9,FThere will also be a tripling of
OL,10,Finvestment in free breakfast clubs,
OL,11,F#1.8 billion for the expansion of
OL,12,Fgovernment-funded childcare, and #44
OL,13,Fmillion to support kinship and foster
OL,14,Fcarers.
OL,16,FAnother #15 million has been pledged
OL,17,Ffor a new scheme placing nurseries in
OL,18,Fschool classrooms. The first phase of
OL,19,Fthe programme will see 300 new or
OL,20,Fexpanded nurseries introduced in
OL,21,Fclassrooms across England.
