OL,3,CBudget 2024: What do we know and what
OL,4,Cdoes it mean?
OL,6,FDebt rule changes
OL,8,FReeves has already confirmed it will
OL,9,Fchange the way debt is measured to
OL,10,Fopen the door for the government to
OL,11,Fspend billions more on infrastructure,
OL,12,Fsuch as railways, roads, hospitals and
OL,13,Fnew prisons.
OL,15,FShe is expected to target public
OL,16,Fsector net financial liabilities
OL,17,F(PSNFL) as her new measure of debt
OL,18,Frather than the current yardstick of
OL,19,Funderlying public sector net debt.
